articles.title: Box Office: Bob Marley ‘One Love’ Jamming to $46M Opening, ‘Madame Web’ Spinning Out With $24M - Hollywood Reporter
articles.description: 'Madame Web,' based on a lesser-known Marvel character Sony has rights to because of its Spider-Man deal, is the latest superhero movie to flail as a pic about a musical icon steals Presidents Day weekend.
